com.ethercis.servicemanager.service

Class ServiceManagerBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ethercis.servicemanager.service.ServiceManagerBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    I_ServiceManager

    public class ServiceManagerBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements I_ServiceManager
    Base class to load Services.

    A typical syntax in the services.properties file is: 

       MimeSubscribeService[ContentLenFilter][1.0]=\
       com.privantis.engine.mime.demo.ContentLenFilter,\
       DEFAULT_MAX_LEN=200,DEFAULT_MIN_LEN=20,classpath=mime.jar
